Bring all your friends and family to our first FREE VIETNAMESE EVENT starring the local May Saigon Band with special guest singers Tam Hao, Nguyen Huy Hoang, and Marilyn Pham on Saturday, November 14th from 8:30pm to 12:30am at Stones Gambling Hall.

FREE LIVE VIET BAND event for 21 & over! Come out enjoy the show and party with us while showing your support to your local Viet band! Please help share this event page and invite all your friends and family! Hope to see everyone then!